commitResults.messageTitle: Split command format to simple and complex
commitResults.messageBody: Originally there was only COMMAND_FORMAT. This has been changed to SIMPLE_COMMAND_FORMAT and COMPLEX_COMMAND_FORMAT to better handle the new incoming commands for job and candidates.Simple commands refer to commands with only 1 word (help and exit). Complex commands refer to commands with multiple command words (delete can, edit job etc.).
